---
title: Korean-Style Tofu & Garlic Brown Rice with Sesame Greens & Sriracha Mayo
description: If you're familiar with bibimbap, the Korean “mixed rice” dish, then you'll love this HelloFresh plant-based version.
So, divvy up the fragrant brown rice, pile on the tofu and toppings, then mix it all together for a glorious fusion of flavours and textures.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-tofu-garlic-rice-d7d95193.jpg
